Installation Instructions

You must have software such as:

   - PERL
   - M4 
   - AUTOCONF 
   - MAKE
   - AUTOMAKE
   - LIBTOOL

Instructions for installing this software you can find on the internet
 
There are two ways to install:

First:
   - clone the repository
   - git clone https://github.com/KrzychuPOL/WDSO-KZ
   - run ./configure
   - if there aren't any errors, run "make"
   - use "sudo make install" in your console
Second: 
   - go to the repository and download the file with the .zip extension
   - unzip it and enter the unpacked folder
   - Follow the steps from first way 

In the repository you can find three versions of the file, each in a different issues
INSTALL EACH ONE IN THE SAME WAY
